# API Testing with REST Client
# Usage: Install "REST Client" extension in VS Code
# Click "Send Request" above each request

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
# For VPS, change to: http://legislatie.issuemonitoring.ro

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### API Documentation
# Opens in browser
GET {{baseUrl}}/docs

### Get All Acte (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/acte?limit=10&offset=0

### Get Single Act by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/acte/1

### Get Act with Articles
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/acte/1?include_articole=true

### Search Acte by Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/acte?tip_act=LEGE

### Search Acte by Year
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/acte?an=2024

### Search Acte by Number
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/acte?numar=123

### Get All Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/categories

### Create Category
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nume": "Test Category",
  "descriere": "Category created via REST Client"
}

### Assign Category to Act
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/acte/1/categories/1

### Export Act for Analysis
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/acte/1/export-for-analysis

### Get Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stats
